# File Description
- cleaned_output.csv: TMDB movie title and movie ID list.
- cleaned_out_v2.csv: UpdatedTMDB movie title and movie ID list for correct movie id codes.
- film_details.csv: Academy Award winning film metadata for top 15 billed cast, director, genre, release_date, and budget pulled through API. 
- film_details_v2.csv Correct movie ids for Academy Award winning films in scope for top 15 billed cast, director, genre, release_date, and budget pulled through API. 
- film_details_v3.csv: Removed missing movie id, reorganized columns, and top 15 billed cast members split into 15 columns. 

# Data Specific Information
- film_details.csv: 6 Skipped films; five skipped due to incorrect movie ID code and one due to not in database. 
- film_details_v2.csv: Fixed incorrect movie ID Code, and movie ID 35430 (Tinker Tailor Soldier Spy)
- film_details_v3.csv: Removed movie ID 35430 from analysis
- My personal TMDB API key was removed from code. To run code TMDB API key is needed. 

